<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- <span class="c3">{إِنْ يَشَأْ يُذْهِبْكُمْ وَيَسْتَخْلِفْ مِنْ بَعْدِكُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٣٣]</span>: <span class="c2">«أعلام الموقعين»</span> ١/ ٢٨٩<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
